data.description: This newly renovated four bedroom, three bathroom home is waiting for you! The home has recently been painted both inside and out, new bathroom counter tops and carpets in the bedrooms. The kitchen has a pantry and brand new Whirlpool appliances. The master bathroom has large tub, separate walk-in shower and dual sinks. One of the bathrooms can be used a future pool bath. Nice long paved driveway with pull off for extra parking as well as a basketball hoop for some family fun.  The 2.27 acres provides ample opportunities for great outdoor living including future buildings, pond, pool, and much more!  Large screened porch off of the living rooms as well as a large concrete patio for entertaining.  MOVE IN READY. DON"T DELAY... WON"T LAST LONG AT THIS PRICE!!!!!
